# =============================================================================
# .gitignore - blitzy-chess monorepo
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Root-level ignore rules covering BOTH subprojects:
#   - backend/   FastAPI app, hand-built chess engine, Python venv, tests
#   - frontend/  Vite + React + TypeScript single-page application
#
# Generated, installed, and downloaded artifacts are never committed:
# virtual environments, node_modules, build output, tool caches, the
# downloaded opening book / Syzygy tablebases, and self-play recordings.
#
# Intentionally TRACKED (do NOT ignore):
#   - frontend/package-lock.json  (lockfile for reproducible installs)
#   - **/.gitkeep                 (placeholders that keep runtime dirs present)
# Patterns are grouped under comment headers, one pattern per line.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Python / backend
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Byte-compiled, optimized, and cached Python files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Packaging and build artifacts
*.egg
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/

# Virtual environments (root-level and backend-local copies)
.venv/
venv/
env/
backend/.venv/
backend/venv/

# Test and lint tool caches
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Coverage reports
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Node / frontend
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Installed dependencies
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/

# Frontend build output (generic dist/ lives in the Python section above)
frontend/dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Vite caches and local environment overrides
.vite/
*.local
frontend/.env.local

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
*.log

# NOTE: frontend/package-lock.json is intentionally NOT ignored - the lockfile
# is committed so dependency installs are reproducible (AAP section 0.3.3).

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Chess data and generated artifacts (downloaded / runtime - never committed)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Polyglot opening book (fetched by `make download-book` / `make init`)
backend/books/*.bin

# Syzygy endgame tablebases (fetched by `make download-syzygy`)
backend/tables/*
*.rtbw
*.rtbz

# Self-play screen recordings and annotated transcripts (runtime output)
backend/games/*.mp4
backend/games/*.md

# Playwright automation artifacts
backend/playwright-report/
backend/test-results/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor / OS noise
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment variable files (may contain secrets - never committed)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Keep runtime-populated directories trackable via placeholder files.
# Placed LAST so these re-inclusions are never overridden by a later pattern.
# Works because the runtime dirs above ignore their CONTENTS (e.g.
# `backend/tables/*`) rather than the directory itself, so .gitkeep can be
# re-included.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
!.gitkeep
!**/.gitkeep
